            <h5>Distribution of Ram and buck for Breeding</h5>
            <p>The Corporation has maintained sheep breed viz. Deccani & Madgyal and Osmanabadi Goat at farms. The improvied Rams and Bucks are produced at farms and supply to the Sheep & Goat Breeders under vaccines of Government schemes for improvement of local Sheep & Goat.</p>
