            <h5>Machine Sharing Programme</h5>
            <p>The Corporation is propogating shearing of sheep by machine. The corporation is providing machine shearing facilities to the nominal cost sheep breedrs by charges Rs. 1.50/- per sheep.</p>
            <hr />
            <h5>Organization of Sheep & Goat Farmers Meet</h5>
            <p>	The Corporation is organizing Shepherds Melava at vaccines places and the providing information regarding Sheep & Goat rearing, Breeding, Feeding and management. The corporation has published pamphlet regarding vaccines sheeps implementing on the corporation.  </p>
            <hr />
            <h5>Production of Fodder, Seeds and Grasses</h5>
            <p>The corporation is producing fodder seed and Grasses and supply to the Sheep & Goat Breedars and Farmers under vaccines Government schemes. </p>
            <hr />
            <h5>Sheep & Goat rearing Trainings</h5>
            <p>To Create self amploment in rural area of the state. The Corporation is conductings 3 days Sheep & Goat Managment training at our 10 Sheep & Goat developments farms training fees Rs. 500/- at farms and Rs. 2000/- at pune.</p>
