            <p>The Corporation is providing wool waving traning at wool utilazation centre pune and aslo wevining traning centre at Ranjani, Dist-Sangali and Padegaon, Dist-Aurangabad. The corporation is producing woollen articals auch as Blankets, Chaddar, carpet, Ghongadi, Satranji, Namada and other at there traninig centre.</p>
